#Not Done yet: The Kiriton Flight related stuff.
#	Kiriton Racial Traits:
#	•  A Kiriton cannot wear armor greater than leather if they intend to Fly.  Leather and padded armor decreases their
#	•  flight maneuverability from Good to Poor; any greater armor makes it impossible to fly. Any armor worn must
#	have holes for the wings to be exposed, resulting in a –1 reduction to the AC value of the armor (To a minimum
#	of 1).
#	•  Kiritons have good flight maneuverability, with a speed of 40 feet. If their
#	wings become wet (for example, soaked in a rainstorm) their maneuverability drops down to Poor with a speed
#	of 20 feet.

